section.section:
In this section, a "health care provider" means:
An acupuncturist;
An audiologist;
A chiropractor;
A dietitian;
A dentist;
An electrologist;
A health care facility that is:
A massage therapist;
A mortician;
A nurse;
A nutritionist;
An occupational therapist;
An optometrist;
A physical therapist;
A physician;
A podiatrist;
A professional counselor;
A psychologist;
A social worker; and
A speech-language pathologist.
